    "title": "Entry-Level Fleet Manager at Expeditors India Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Expeditors India Advisory Limited invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Fleet Manager at our Jaipur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Expeditors India Advisory Limited:\nExpeditors India Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee end-to-end logistics operations for timely delivery\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Prepare MIS reports on delivery performance and SLA adherence\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n• Track shipments in real-time and resolve delivery exceptions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in 3PL Management\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in TMS\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Expeditors India Advisory Limited!",
